 This is more suggestive of the impact of conditional contracts as in both cases now farmers are exposed to the significant buyer.
 Note that we can block on pairs to get rid of pair all characteristics that would be the same for both of these farmers (like distance to trader etc)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
repeat analysis for subgroups of farmers that are actually selling to WFP as the treatment variable.
 If the effect becomes bigger,
 that would indicate any effect really comes from the policy.
 This can also be done for traders.
 
\end_layout

